Wed Apr  8 09:01:49 UTC 2026 - Dirk Müller <dmueller@suse.com>

- update to 0.11.0:
  * This release refactors a lot of the internals to break up
    conversion and validation. This should not be noticeable
    except for better error messages in some cases.
  * Test on some downstream projects.
  * Remove some PEP 621 terminology

